<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Understeer F1 | Free Live Streams & Discord Community</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:opsz,wght@14..32,300;14..32,400;14..32,600;14..32,700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background-color: #0a0a0a;
            color: #e0e0e0;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        /* Header / Hero */
        .hero {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 4rem 1rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f0f0f 0%, #1a1a1a 100%);
            border-radius: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            border: 1px solid rgba(229, 9, 20, 0.3);
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e50914, #ff4d4d);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            color: transparent;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto 2rem;
            color: #b0b0b0;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #e50914;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            padding: 0.9rem 2rem;
            border-radius: 40px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(229, 9, 20, 0.3);
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background: #ff1a1a;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(229, 9, 20, 0.4);
        }

        /* Features grid */
        .features {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
            margin: 4rem 0;
        }

        .feature-card {
            background: #111111;
            border-radius: 1.5rem;
            padding: 1.8rem;
            transition: transform 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
            border: 1px solid #222;
        }

        .feature-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            border-color: #e50914;
        }

        .feature-icon {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .feature-card h3 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .feature-card p {
            color: #aaa;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        /* How it works */
        .how-it-works {
            background: #0c0c0c;
            border-radius: 2rem;
            padding: 2.5rem;
            margin: 3rem 0;
            text-align: center;
            border: 1px solid #222;
        }

        .how-it-works h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .steps {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }

        .step {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 200px;
            padding: 1rem;
        }

        .step-number {
            width: 48px;
            height: 48px;
            background: #e50914;
            color: white;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .step h4 {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .step p {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #aaa;
        }

        /* Footer */
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem 0;
            border-top: 1px solid #222;
            margin-top: 3rem;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: #666;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                padding: 1rem;
            }
            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 2.2rem;
            }
            .hero {
                padding: 2rem 1rem;
            }
            .feature-card {
                padding: 1.2rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="hero">
            <h1>🏎️ UNDERSTEER F1</h1>
            <p>Live streams of every Formula 1 session – free, no ads, no spoilers.<br>Join our Discord and watch with the community.</p>
            <a href="https://discord.gg/YOUR_INVITE_CODE" class="btn" target="_blank">Join the Grid →</a>
        </div>

        <div class="features">
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">📡</div>
                <h3>Free Live Streams</h3>
                <p>Every practice, qualifying, and race streamed in high quality. No subscription needed.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">🚫</div>
                <h3>Spoiler‑Free</h3>
                <p>Our stage system hides channels until the session is live. Quali only during quali, race only during race.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">🏎️</div>
                <h3>Team Roles</h3>
                <p>Show your colours with constructor roles – Ferrari, McLaren, Red Bull and more.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">🗣️</div>
                <h3>Active Community</h3>
                <p>Chat in text or voice during sessions, share memes, and enjoy the race together.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="how-it-works">
            <h2>How to Watch</h2>
            <div class="steps">
                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-number">1</div>
                    <h4>Join Discord</h4>
                    <p>Click the button above and accept the invite.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-number">2</div>
                    <h4>Quick Verify</h4>
                    <p>Solve a simple math captcha in DMs – keeps bots out.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-number">3</div>
                    <h4>Pick Your Team</h4>
                    <p>Choose a constructor role in #role-select.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-number">4</div>
                    <h4>Enjoy the Race</h4>
                    <p>When the session is live, the channel appears. No spoilers.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 2rem 0;">
            <a href="https://discord.gg/YOUR_INVITE_CODE" class="btn" target="_blank">Join Now – It's Free</a>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>No paywalls. No spam. Just F1 with friends.<br>Understeer F1 – we stream every session, live.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
